May 2023 ➝ April 2020

traded our dogs for kids 😉
we have officially moved out of our first home & it feels so bittersweet. I’m so excited to be in a home that better suits us, but I’ll always love the home we brought our babies home to 🫶🏼
after so many years of infertility, I’m still pinching myself over the fact that I have two perfect little girls + I get to be their mama🫶🏼

we had the best day celebrating our little wild flower 🌼

she has been singing “Happy Birthday to Austyn” for monthsss & yesterday was finally her day. She loved getting it sung to her so much, she made us all sing it twice 🫶🏼
four weeks with our Zae 🫶🏼

HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO THE DANCING QUEEN!! two years of dancing with my best friend. The girl who healed my heart + brought me back to life after the darkest, hardest years of my life. I’m so honored to be your mom, Austyn Brelyn 🌼 05.22.21 will always hold an extremely special place in my heart 🤍
mini me number one 🌼
the best girl dad we could have ever dreamed of 🫶🏼 we love you so much @hashtagtaylor !!!
